{
  "spec": {
    "title": "CSS Color Adjustment Module Level 1",
    "url": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "used color scheme",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#used-color-scheme",
      "html": "To determine the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"used-color-scheme\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">used color scheme</dfn>,\n\t\tgiven a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme-support\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme-support⑥\">color scheme support</a> <var>support</var>\n\t\tand a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme-preference\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme-preference②\">color scheme preference</a> <var>preference</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>support</var> is null,\nor none of the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②①\">color schemes</a> in <var>support</var>\nare supported by the UA,\nreturn the UA default <span id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②②\">color scheme</span>,\nand annotate that this <span id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②③\">color scheme</span> was <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme-default\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme-default①\">defaulted</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>preference</var> is no preference,\nreturn the first supported <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②④\">color scheme</a> in <var>support</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>preference</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②⑤\">color scheme</a> is in <var>support</var>\nand supported by the UA,\nreturn that <span id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②⑥\">color scheme</span>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>support</var> is flagged as sole support,\nreturn the first supported <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②⑦\">color scheme</a> in <var>support</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>preference</var> is an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme-overriding-preference\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme-overriding-preference\">overriding preference</a>,\nreturn <var>preference</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②⑧\">color scheme</a>.\nIf this <span id=\"ref-for-color-scheme②⑨\">color scheme</span> is used as an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#element-color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-element-color-scheme⑤\">element color scheme</a>,\nalso <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#override-the-color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-override-the-color-scheme①\">override the color scheme</a> on the element\nto this <span id=\"ref-for-color-scheme③⓪\">color scheme</span>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise,\nreturn the first supported <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#color-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-color-scheme③①\">color scheme</a> in <var>support</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "set emulated forced colors theme data",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#set-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"set-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">set emulated forced colors theme data</dfn>, given\n\t<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window-navigable\" id=\"ref-for-window-navigable\">navigable</a> <var>navigable</var> and an <var>emulatedThemeData</var>:",
      "rationale": "assert",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Assert <var>emulatedThemeData</var> is <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#enumdef-forcedcolorsmodeautomationtheme\" id=\"ref-for-enumdef-forcedcolorsmodeautomationtheme①\">ForcedColorsModeAutomationTheme</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>traversable</var> be <var>navigable</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-top\" id=\"ref-for-nav-top\">top-level traversable</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>traversable</var> is not null:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>traversable</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#emulated-forced-colors-theme-data\" id=\"ref-for-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data①\">emulated forced colors theme data</a> to\n<var>emulatedThemeData</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>UAs must consider this a change that requires style recalculation.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "get emulated forced colors theme data",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#get-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get emulated forced colors theme data</dfn>, given <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#enumdef-forcedcolorsmodeautomationtheme\" id=\"ref-for-enumdef-forcedcolorsmodeautomationtheme②\">ForcedColorsModeAutomationTheme</a></code>\n\t\t<var>theme</var>:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>navigable</var> be <var>theme</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global\">relevant global object</a>’s\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window\">associated Document</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#node-navigable\" id=\"ref-for-node-navigable\">node navigable</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>navigable</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>traversable</var> be <var>navigable</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-top\" id=\"ref-for-nav-top①\">top-level traversable</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>traversable</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>traversable</var>’s associated <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-adjust-1/#emulated-forced-colors-theme-data\" id=\"ref-for-emulated-forced-colors-theme-data②\">emulated forced colors theme data</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}